                        <interp inst="t18480131-name-223" type="given" value="SOLOMON"></interp>SOLOMON PEISLEY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, C</hi> 92.) I was sent for, and took the pri<lb></lb>soner—I produce the two half-crowns.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
